    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example boasts a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed for preventative longevity. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing original M-tuned dampers and bushings. Finished in concours-level paint with a pristine interior, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak naturally aspirated performance.",
