    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available now is a museum-quality E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-precision 8,000 RPM valvetrain. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rod bearings and dual-VANOS system have been proactively serviced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission shifts with tactile precision, paired with a factory variable M differential lock for exceptional corner-exit traction. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback only a low-mileage, well-preserved chassis can offer. Finished in a concours-level exterior with a pristine interior, this vehicle is free of any kinetic or cosmetic deficiencies.",
